DOW INSTA STIK EXPANDING FOAM GRAB ADHESIVE GUN GRADE 750ML
fields.description: Fast curing low expansion adhesive. Quick and easy to use, ideal for fixing plasterboard, insulation board, floorboards, shower/bathroom boards and most common building substrates. No waste or mess. For professional use only. Coverage per can: 15m².

fields.name: GRIPFILL SOLVENT-FREE WHITE 350ML
fields.description: Solvent-free alternative to the brand-leading Gripfill. Bonds plasterboard, skirting boards, electrical conduit, stone, ferrous and non-ferrous metals. Excellent adhesion and bonding strength.

fields.name: SOUDAL ADHESIVE FOAM HAND-HELD 750ML
fields.description: Suitable for use as an adhesive, ideal for fixing large sheet materials, or as an expanding filler for large holes, gaps and cavities.

fields.name: NO NONSENSE I CAN'T BELIEVE IT'S NOT NAILS ADHESIVE WHITE 290ML
fields.description: Universal sealant and adhesive with hybrid technology. Free of isocyanates, solvents and silicones, whilst resistant to UV, moisture, mould and weather. Does not crack, shrink or bubble and is non-corrosive towards metals. Neutral curing, almost odourless and adheres perfectly without a primer on most surfaces. Absorbs acoustic and mechanical vibrations. Remains flexible and is paintable once fully cured. Suitable for interior and exterior applications.

fields.name: YBS AIRTEC REFLECTIVE DOUBLE INSULATION 25 X 1.2M
fields.description: Thin, flexible, easy to install, aluminium bubble insulation membrane. Acts by trapping air within the bubble structure while creating low emissivity air spaces from foil-faced outer layers, enhancing overall thermal capabilities. Suitable for roofs, walls and floors.

fields.name: YBS THERMAWRAP GENERAL PURPOSE INSULATION 10 X 1.05M
fields.description: High quality LDPE bubble membrane with aluminium reflective foil surfaces on both sides. Offers the same thermal resistance as 55mm polystyrene and equivalent to 35mm PIR insulation board. Can be used for refurbishments, conversions and DIY applications including walls, floors, roofs, lofts, garages, sheds, caravans, boats, pet homes and greenhouses. Lightweight and easy to install with no harmful particles.

fields.name: YBS SUPERQUILT MULTI-LAYER REFLECTIVE FOIL INSULATION 10 X 1.5M
fields.description: Multi-layer reflective foil insulation for roofs, walls and floors. Made with aluminium for maximum thermal performance, the reflective properties keep the living space warm in winter and cool in summer with effective solar over-heating barrier. Lightweight and flexible. Fast and simple installation without any harmful fibres or particles.

fields.name: YBS BREATHERQUILT 2-IN-1 MEMBRANE & INSULATION 10 X 1.2M
fields.description: 2-in-1 breathable multi-layer insulation blanket. Lightweight and flexible making it easy to install with no harmful fibres or particles. Provides optimum thermal resistance, ideal for new build and refurbishment. Manufactured in the UK.

fields.name: FISCHER FSA SLEEVE ANCHORS SILVER 10 X 60MM M8 20 PACK
fields.description: Sleeve anchor with hexagon bolt head. Setting depth indicator for correct installation. Cone shape and sleeve cut-out. Guaranteed reliability and performance. Suitable for most brick, block and concrete.

fields.name: Easydrive EASYDRIVE COUNTERSUNK CONCRETE SCREWS 7.5 X 80MM 100 PACK
fields.description: Ideal for fixing uPVC and timber frames directly to masonry.

fields.name: RAWLPLUG NYLON HAMMER-IN FIXINGS 6 X 60MM 100 PACK
fields.description: Very simple to use with fast installation. For fast, repetitive fixing with minimal screwdriver work. Ideal for fixing skirting, stud battens to walls and long runs of shelf supports. High quality nylon.

fields.name: FISCHER SELF-DRILL PLASTERBOARD FIXINGS METAL 35MM 100 PACK
fields.description: Easy self-drilling plug can be drilled straight into plasterboard. Supplied with screws and drill bit.

fields.name: FOREST DOUBLE-SLATTED FENCE PANEL 6 X 6' PACK OF 3

Features slats mounted alternately on the front and back of the panel. Offers privacy whilst still letting some light and air flow through. Ideal for boundaries, screening and partitioning.

fields.name: FOREST PRAGUE LATTICE CURVED TOP FENCE PANELS 6 X 5' PACK OF 5

fields.description: A contemporary stone paving slab that guarantees minimum base technical performance for water absorption and front resistance, meaning your paving looks good for longer.

fields.name: Marshalls Argent Coarse Light Grey Paving Slab 600 X 600 X 38 Mm - 9m2 Pack

fields.name: EVOLUTION CIRCULAR SAW BLADE 210 X 25.4MM 24T
fields.description: Cost-effective blade featuring RAGE technology. For cutting steel, aluminium, wood and plastic. Cuts nail-embedded wood easily and cuts steel with virtually no sparks or heat. Collects most wood and metal chippings automatically. Only suitable for use with Evolution circular and mitre saws.

fields.name: BOSCH S1122BF RECIPROCATING SAW BLADES 225MM 5 PACK
fields.description: Reciprocating saw blade for fast flush cuts in metal. For use with reciprocating saws with ½" universal shank systems. Bi-metal blade is ideal for cutting pipes and profiles with a wall thickness from 3mm to 8mm. With a cutting capacity up to 175mm.

fields.name: BOSCH SELF-CUT SPEED FLAT WOOD DRILL BIT SET 8 PCS
fields.description: Self-feeding threaded tip for faster, more accurate drilling, with little exertion or force. Pulls itself into the wood effortlessly and extremely quickly due to its self-feeding threaded tip.

fields.name: DEWALT DCD776D2T- GB 18V 2.0AH LI-ION XR CORDLESS COMBI DRILL
fields.description: Compact drill driver with XR Li-ion battery technology, designed for efficiency and making applications faster. Improved ergonomic design and rubber grip increases comfort and provides maximum control. Supplied with multi-voltage charger for all XR Li-ion slide pack batteries. Supplied in a TSTAK kit box.

fields.name: EVOLUTION R255SMS 255MM ELECTRIC SINGLE-BEVEL SLIDING MITRE SAW 220-240V
fields.description: Compound mitre saw supplied with a multifunction TCT blade that can easily cut through wood, aluminium, plastic and steel, even if nails are still embedded in the material. The multipurpose blade cuts cleanly and leaves no burrs on steel. Easy to assemble and use, as the laser cutting guide helps get the highest possible accuracy. The supplied clamp also keeps the workpiece in place.

fields.name: STANLEY FATMAX MIXED SCREWDRIVER SET 12 PCS
fields.description: Large diameter handle with soft-grip for added grip and torque. Colour-coded ends for ease of selection in the toolbox. With high quality chrome vanadium steel bar moulded to the handle for added durability.

fields.name: IRWIN JACK 8TPI WOOD SAW 20" (500MM)
fields.description: Razor-sharp triple-ground teeth for cutting all materials. Cuts on the push and pull. Water-based lacquer gives up to 4 times more rust protection. Comfortable handle for prolonged use.

fields.name: JSP EVO2 MID PEAK SLIP-RATCHET VENTED SAFETY HELMET WHITE
fields.description: Modern, fully peaked shell style helmet with ventilation holes and inner adjustable harness. Features 3-point height adjustability on rear of harness, and 2-point adjustability on front. One size fits all.

fields.name: SITE KF320 NITRILE FOAM COATED GLOVES RED / BLACK LARGE
fields.description: Breathable, nitrile foam-coated gloves with comfortable nylon and spandex blend liner. Developed for high dexterity when precision handling is required. Offers excellent grip in dry, wet and oily conditions.

fields.name: DEWALT CONCEALER CONCEALER PREMIUM SAFETY GOGGLES
fields.description: Polycarbonate, wraparound lens with 180° field of vision and ventilation ports. Provides protection against dust and liquid, including molten metal. Lightweight design.

fields.name: 3M PELTOR OPTIME III EAR DEFENDERS 35DB SNR
